      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Biology (Sci)              : Unified view of form and function in animals and plants. Focus on how the laws of chemistry and physics illuminate biological processes relating to the acquisition of energy and materials and their use in movement, growth, development, reproduction and responses to environmental stress.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Winter 2015          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        Rajinder S Dhindsa (Winter)                  </p>

    
