  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Earth System Science              : An understanding of the biological, chemical and physical fundamentals of the Earth system and how the different components interact. The mechanisms controlling interactions between reservoirs are quantitatively investigated. Special emphasis on the development and response of the Earth system to perturbations.          </p>

