      Earth &amp; Planetary Sciences              : Geological mapping of selected areas, preparation of maps, reports from field notes, aerial photographs, etc.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Winter 2015          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        Andrew J Hynes (Winter)                  </p>

    
